size}/226662_2.png","created_at":"2024-07-05T14:48:25.796Z","cooked":"<p>Our team just started with swerve this season (REV MaxSwerve). We abused it. Badly and we are seeing wear on specific components that we are replacing/upgrading. We saved up and debated it for years before we picked this swerve for the price point. Now having gotten a taste we will be looking to switch up to a better system as our resources allow. (Getting into MK series).</p>
<p>The question for us is when? We can make do with the REV MaxSwerve, but if we did have the money to buy a second newer system we would.</p>
